data.description: "Welcome to your dream home in Suwanee, GA! This spacious and beautifully updated residence features 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The finished basement is a versatile addition, offering a teen or in-law suite for added convenience.  Enjoy the modern touch of updated bathrooms and kitchen, providing a fresh and stylish atmosphere. New carpet adds a cozy feel throughout, and the entire home has been freshly painted, making it move-in ready.  Situated in Suwanee, this home is not only a haven of comfort but also located in an area with highly rated schools, ensuring an excellent education for your family. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your own. Schedule a viewing today and envision the possibilities of calling this place home!"
